04/01/2010
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- A gunman opened fire at a night club in Peja/Pec in western Kosovo late Saturday (January 2nd), killing one person and injuring three others.
Police spokesperson Avni Gjevukaj said on Sunday that the motive is unclear, and that officers are working to identify the shooter.
(Evropa e Lire, Telegrafi, RTK - 02/01/10)
